title: #172: Begrudgingly Domesticated (@Jason23Nash)
itunes:title: Begrudgingly Domesticated with Jason Nash
description: Jason Nash met me at his friends deluxe apartment in the skyiyiy to talk about marriage. Nash has always been, shall we say, rageful about his marriage onstage. It was nice to get a good honest negative view of marriage from someone who is still in one. Intro from Hong Kong.
